What were we supposed to do? I am a survivor of domestic violence Abusive people are now easy to spot, they talk different, they look at you different, they word their sentences different. It's kind of neat, I can see them coming and avoid them.

Just wanted to warn you the beautiful and rich AH is no good, stay away! You can believe me because I'm an absolute nobody. I can just see it. 
Love, your fan,
Blah blah blah
I'm sure he would have taken that seriously! (His staff would say "creeper alert! Time for a restraining order!")
I felt bad watching it knowing what would happen. But I also felt useless.
